          <div class="faq-answer">Writesonic is an AI writing platform launched in 2020 and Y Combinator-backed (W21). It bundles an AI article writer, a ChatGPT-style research tool called Chatsonic, a no-code chatbot builder called Botsonic, and an AI-search visibility tracker that monitors ChatGPT, Perplexity, and Google AI Overviews.</div>
